# Local Testing of Solidity Files

**Testing Solidity on Forked Base Mainnet**

When testing Solidity, be sure to fork Base Mainnet and run the tests. Example:

```bash
forge test --match-path pathToTests/TestFileName.t.sol --fork-url https://base-mainnet.infura.io/v3/94897ae46fe145559d8e5f989b501afb --fork-block-number 29886571 -vvv --via-ir
```